      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 50,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "冬の方がワキガ臭い...\n原因は◯◯の増殖!?",
      "heading_level": "h2",
      "tag_hint": "h2",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 51,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "「冬の方がニオイが濃いな...」",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 52,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "ワキガの人なら誰しも一度はそう思いますよね。",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 53,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "実は冬の方がニオイがキツくなる原因は....",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 54,
      "block_type": "image",
      "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/uploads/article_photo/photo/6353768/de7adea4-e823-4589-acf2-3c8139ccfc80.png",
      "alt_text": "",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 55,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "そもそもなんでワキガ臭が発生するかは",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 56,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "知っていますか？",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 57,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "ご察しの通り、",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 58,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "汗を菌が分解するときに",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 59,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "あのいや〜なニオイが発生するんです。",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 60,
      "block_type": "video",
      "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/uploads/article_photo/photo/5784499/e6e3f34f-aaf9-4007-bfff-bde0de62a66a.mp4",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 61,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "冬は重ね着や通気性の悪い服を着ることから",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 62,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "温度・湿度が夏より上昇。",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 63,
      "block_type": "image",
      "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/uploads/article_photo/photo/6353867/e35e0545-5cc8-41ea-ad9c-8a66d8a45796.png",
      "alt_text": "",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 64,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "出典：https://lidea.today/articles/641",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 65,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "温度と湿度はワキガ菌の恰好の繁殖場所。",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 66,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "たちまち増えていくんです。",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 67,
      "block_type": "video",
      "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/uploads/article_photo/photo/5785034/883afc50-081b-43c3-9e12-0ae58ccafa94.mp4",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 68,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "さらに！",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 69,
      "block_type": "text",
      "content": "分泌される汗も夏よりも濃縮されているんです。",
      "heading_level": "body",
      "tag_hint": "p",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 70,
      "block_type": "image",
      "media_url": "https://file.mysquadbeyond.com/uploads/article_photo/photo/6353936/328784f4-f979-44bf-ae71-36ee3a44ff5b.png",
      "alt_text": "",
      "is_cta_block": false
    },
    {
      "order": 71,
